Qualcomm has detailed its latest fast-charging standard, Quick Charge 4+. “Quick Charge 4+ includes all the benefits of Quick Charge 4, plus more,” said Qualcomm. The new enhancements include: The features allow devices to charge up to 15% faster, or 30% more efficiently, than compared to Quick Charge 4. The first device to include Quick Charge 4+ support is the ZTE Nubia Z17, a smartphone with a 3,200mAh battery, Snapdragon 835 chip, and 8GB of RAM. 